        <span class="f-eyebrow">The flood question</span>
        <h3>Answered straight, block by block</h3>
        <p>Much of the interior grid sits in Zone X (flood insurance optional, often smart); the
        blocks along Coffee Pot Bayou and the open bay carry AE ratings where coverage is required
        and priced to the elevation certificate. Every listing here should be checked per-address &mdash;
        we do it on the FEMA flood layer, free, before you offer. (SAMPLE summary &mdash; the per-address
        lookup ships at Build.)</p>
